The paper discusses the use of millimeter wave frequencies for wireless networks, which falls under the category of networked and internet-connected systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of antenna arrays and spatial multiplexing, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT). The use of millimeter wave frequencies is also a topic related to millimeter wave technology (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the feasibility of wide-area cellular networks, which is a topic related to control and optimization (cs.MA) and systems and control (cs.SY).
